Shine with glamour in a graceful dress from Milano Formals E1463. Crafted in lustrous taffeta fabric this gorgeous dress done in sleeveless style and a V-neck neckline is sure to flatter your figure. Highlighting the waist is wide finely ruched waistband with floral embellishment on one side. The graceful A-line silhouette skirt has added a pinch of playfulness. Be the darling, creates a fun and exciting look in Milano Formals. Be a sure standout in this fabulous creation from Milano Formals E1730. The one shoulder bodice is pinched with asymmetrical wrapping ruched fabric creating a flattering silhouette on this cocktail length dress. The floral motif at the beginning of the semi-wide strap has added a feminine touch. The A-line skirt is enhanced with shirred sheer overlay creating an illusion hemline. Be ready to fascinate everyone in this ultimately chic dress by Milano formals. This style also comes in a romantic long version in Milano Formals E1729.
